@database ColoradjustClass
@index "Classes.guide/Main"

@Node Main "RxMUI - Coloradjust Class"


Coloradjust class    @{"Index" link "Classes.guide/Main"} @{"Super" link "GroupClass.guide/Main"}
@{u}                                                             @{uu}

  The Coloradjust class is used to create a group with various
  objects that permits the user to modify a colour.

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Attributes@{ub}

  @{fg shine}Blue@{fg text}
  S ISGN
  It is a 4 bytes max size packed char string 32 bits Blue
  component, e.g. "FF000000"x; it is notified as a N

  @{fg shine}Green@{fg text}
  S ISGN
  It is a 4 bytes max size packed char string 32 bits Green
  component

  @{fg shine}ModeID@{fg text}
  S ISGN
  It is a 4 bytes max size packed char string representing a
  screen Mode ID.

  @{fg shine}Red@{fg text}
  S ISGN
  It is a 4 bytes max size packed char string 32 bits Red
  component

  @{u}                                                        @{uu}

 @{b}Methods@{ub}

  None defined

@EndNode
